title: Video: Eyedress – Don’t Disappear
content:
Eyedress’ videos seem to be getting better and better.

The visuals for his track Don’t Disappear are playful, quietly sombre and actual pretty rich in subject matter. He seems to be throwing a load of stuff at the wall at the moment, and a large proportion of the ‘stuff’, is sticking.
